Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's crazy. I'm about to start college.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.93,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不知道为什么  我不知道我想做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't know why. I have no idea what I want to do yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.93,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你像我这么大时知道自己想做什么吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Did you know what you wanted to do at my age?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.27,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}知道  我想当兵
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah, I wanted to be a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:46.98,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}像我这么大时
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.74,0:12:46.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}At my age?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.98,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}比你现在还小一点
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Even before your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.15,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你喜欢当兵吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:55.65,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我曾有过毕生最好的几个朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.58,0:12:55.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Well, I had some of the best friends I ever had for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.09,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有你在这里问东问西
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's gonna be real quiet around here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.57,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这里会变得特别安静
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}without you asking all these questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.83,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-你肯定能扛住  -是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.83,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- I'm sure you'll survive. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.47,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太阳要落山了  我只能再骑一小时了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The sun's setting. I only have about an hour left to ride, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.17,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-为什么  -我得去安东尼娅家
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Why is that? - I have to go to Antonia's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.52,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她邀请秋天要去上大学的人
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}She's throwing this thing for the guys
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.30,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一起聚会
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}who are going to college in the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.51,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你干嘛不请他们来这里
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why don't you invite them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:22.97,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.07,0:13:22.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.30,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}带他们来这里
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Bring them over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.27,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还记得上次他们来吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Remember what happened last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.68,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-你把他们吓坏了  -为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- You freaked them out. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.95,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为你一直瞪着他们
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Because you wouldn't stop staring at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.11,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.32,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我有时会那样  但不是故意的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah, I do that sometimes, but it's not intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.63,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢邀请  但安东尼娅已经搞定了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.54,0:13:39.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Thank you, but Antonia's got it covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.28,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们就在这里聚会  行吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We're just gonna have it there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.49,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}带他们看看地道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Show them the tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.08,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.08,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.45,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}带他们看看地道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.45,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Show them the tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.25,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你从不让别人进地道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You don't let anybody go in the tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.92,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的  但他们是你的朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.68,0:13:55.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, but they're your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.25,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以他们可以
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}so they're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.44,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-行  好  -带他们看看地道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Okay, cool. Yeah. - Yeah, show them the tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.63,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那会很好玩的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah, that would be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.30,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我以后肯定会想念和你一起骑马的时光
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm really gonna miss riding with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.77,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我也会想念的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm gonna miss riding with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.44,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}准备好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.33,0:14:19.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.91,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是不是很酷  他从不让别人下来
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Isn't this cool? He's never let anyone down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.58,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真疯狂  兄弟
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This is crazy, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.12,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我能适应
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I could get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.84,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我希望她玩得开心
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.84,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I hope she's having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.59,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你从不让我进地道
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.48,0:14:41.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You never let me in the tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:46.47,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你真想进的话  我可以带你转一圈
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.82,0:14:46.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If you really wanna go in, I'll take you on a guided tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:49.39,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不了  谢谢  太脏了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.74,0:14:49.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, thank you. Too dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.85,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}确实
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.85,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.26,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是个聚会的好地方  宝贝
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This is a great place for a party, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.80,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在不行  好吗  我脑子里一堆事
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.80,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Not right now, okay? I have a lot on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.29,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好  我理解
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.77,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-你画的吗  -对
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Did you draw that? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:16.81,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其实是我十岁画的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.77,0:15:16.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I drew that, actually, when I was ten years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.59,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}画得真棒
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.59,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是谁
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.65,0:15:20.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.51,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我得接这个电话
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I got to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.05,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吉赛尔
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gizelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:28.19,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}妹子  你能听见吗  信号不太好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.11,0:15:28.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hey, girl, can you hear me? The reception is not so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.89,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}能  能  我能听见
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, no. Yeah, yeah. I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.22,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都告诉我
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.90,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-加布里埃尔  -怎么
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Gabrielle? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.03,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在这里做什么  你朋友都走了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.03,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What are you doing down here? All of your friends have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.87,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们搞得乱糟糟的  我在清理
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They made a big mess. I'm just cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.99,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}聚会怎样
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.72,0:15:50.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}So, how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.79,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大家都很开心
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.79,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Everyone had a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.17,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们一直问我为什么我叔叔挖了地道
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They kept asking me why my uncle built these tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.88,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你怎么说
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:04.30,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我说你喜欢挖掘  还有点疯癫
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.98,0:16:04.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I said that you like digging and you're a little crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.59,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}挺对的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.93,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我得跟你谈点事
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.77,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我希望你能用开放的心态来看
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And I just want you to have an open mind about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.73,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我得去一趟墨西哥
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I need to go to Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.56,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你为什么想去那里
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why would you want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.53,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为我找到了我爸爸
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.53,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Because I found my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.84,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我朋友吉赛尔  她住在墨西哥
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.84,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}My friend Gizelle, who lives there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.95,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她原来住这里  你记得她吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Well, she used to live here. Do you remember her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:38.71,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我让她帮个忙  她找到了他
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.60,0:16:38.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I asked her for a favor, and she found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.13,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他住在她附近的一个镇里
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.13,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}He lives in a town near hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.59,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约翰叔叔  我必须去
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Uncle John, I have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.65,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我需要听他亲口说出来
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I need to hear it from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.49,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我需要明白他为什么那么做
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I need to understand why he would just do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.18,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为他不是好人
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Because he's not a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.52,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-不可能那么简单  -就那么简单
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.12,0:16:58.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Can't be that simple. - It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.24,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约翰叔叔  我听过那些故事
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.24,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Uncle John, I've heard the stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.70,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道你经历过很多
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.70,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know you've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:05.53,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的世界与你的完全不同
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.71,0:17:05.53,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But my world is a lot different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.17,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}确实  你的更可怕
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, it's not. It's worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.32,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.05,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}人不会无缘无故做坏事
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}People don't just act bad for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.55,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个男人不管有什么理由都不能抛弃家庭
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}There's no reason for a man to throw his family away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.88,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}能有个家庭就够幸运了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.88,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}He's lucky he has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:17.22,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-你为什么这么生气  -因为你不知道这个世界多坏
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.89,0:17:17.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Why are you getting so mad? - Because you don't know how bad it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.26,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道人心能有多黑暗
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know how black a man's heart can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.18,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这世上没有好人  加布里埃尔
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}There's nothing good out there, Gabrielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.31,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也许他变了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Maybe he's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.81,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那种男人不会变  只会变得更坏
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Men like that don't change. It only gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.05,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你就变了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.01,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没变
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.52,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只是努力控制住自己  日日如此
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.52,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm just trying to keep a lid on it, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.61,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约翰叔叔  我需要你信任我
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.53,0:17:32.61,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Uncle John, I need you to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:36.18,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我需要你知道我会做出正确的决定
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.61,0:17:36.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I need you to know that I'm gonna make good decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.85,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我控制不了外面的世界
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.85,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I can't control what's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.81,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你不可能永远保护我
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You can't just protect me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.96,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只要我还有一口气
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.83,0:17:45.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}As long as I'm around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.73,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他就别想再伤害你
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}he's never gonna hurt you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:49.99,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没人能
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.79,0:17:49.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No one is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.76,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你说你做了你认为正确的事  十七岁就离开了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.76,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You said you did what you thought was right and left at 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.33,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没人阻止你
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}and nobody stopped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.91,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我希望他们阻止了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.59,0:17:58.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I wish they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:03.92,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}加布里埃尔  你就像我女儿一样
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.35,0:18:03.92,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gabrielle, I care for you like a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.63,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道你想要答案
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.63,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know you want answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.13,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}稍微等一等
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.13,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Just wait a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.38,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}再长大一点
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Grow up a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.51,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}再多了解这世界一点
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.57,0:18:14.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Know about the world a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.39,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你愿意为我这么做吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Would you do that for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.65,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.02,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.57,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要睡了  晚安
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.08,0:18:30.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm gonna go to bed. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.95,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.30,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只想知道原因
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I just wanna know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.68,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.64,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她想去见她父亲
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}She wants to see her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.96,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}加布里埃尔  我以为我们已经说好了
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gabrielle, I thought we had an understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:15.00,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是啊  是啊  对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.96,0:19:15.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We did. We did. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:17.87,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我考虑了一晚上...
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.01,0:19:17.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But I've been thinking about it all night, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.87,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我现在就想知道答案  不是以后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.87,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I just want answers now, not later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.25,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你怎么找到他的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}How did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.62,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吉赛尔帮了我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gizelle helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:27.96,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吉赛尔
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.98,0:19:27.96,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gizelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.80,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她是想帮我
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.80,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}She's trying to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.74,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个人才更像你的父亲
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.73,0:19:44.74,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That man is more your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.58,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}照顾你  保护你
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.58,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Watching over you, protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.40,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最近这十年  他就是你父亲
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.40,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}These last ten years, he was the father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:50.83,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}玛丽亚  别激动
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.00,0:19:50.83,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Maria, go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.19,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不激动  为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:53.78,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为所以
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.71,0:19:53.78,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Because.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.29,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}够了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.79,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}告诉她
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.79,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:32.82,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.92,0:20:32.82,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.36,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你说得对  我不去了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You're right. I won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.74,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我去安东尼娅家
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.74,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm gonna go to Antonia's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.12,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好的  抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.41,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事的  她还是个孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.41,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all right. She's a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.81,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约翰叔叔
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Uncle John!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.94,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}刚才的事真对不起
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.94,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sorry about everything earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.81,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没关系
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.73,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:37.55,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}快过来
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.28,0:23:37.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:40.72,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}瞧瞧你
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.74,0:23:40.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:58.05,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-要喝点什么吗  -不用  谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:23:55.71,0:23:58.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- You want something to drink? - No, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:23:58.99,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要喝
Dialogue: 1,0:23:58.05,0:23:58.99,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.72,0:24:03.49,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我就坐在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:24:01.72,0:24:03.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll just sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.97,0:24:09.00,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道我能感觉到你在四处打量吧
Dialogue: 1,0:24:06.97,0:24:09.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You know, I can feel you looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.18,0:24:11.13,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 1,0:24:10.18,0:24:11.13,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:12.79,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这房子很棒  对吧
Dialogue: 1,0:24:11.64,0:24:12.79,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's a nice house, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.27,0:24:14.42,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对  挺好的
Dialogue: 1,0:24:13.27,0:24:14.42,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.19,0:24:16.84,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我还能感觉到你在打量我
Dialogue: 1,0:24:15.19,0:24:16.84,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I can feel you looking at me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.98,0:24:18.93,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有
Dialogue: 1,0:24:17.98,0:24:18.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:21.39,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没  你看起来很棒
Dialogue: 1,0:24:19.15,0:24:21.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No. You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.65,0:24:22.97,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道我变了不少
Dialogue: 1,0:24:21.65,0:24:22.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.07,0:24:26.56,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}姐妹  这里的生活不容易
Dialogue: 1,0:24:24.07,0:24:26.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Life down here, it ain't easy, my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.20,0:24:28.35,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你得尽力而为
Dialogue: 1,0:24:27.20,0:24:28.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:30.48,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我明白
Dialogue: 1,0:24:29.20,0:24:30.48,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.16,0:24:34.11,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我非常感激你帮我找我爸爸
Dialogue: 1,0:24:31.16,0:24:34.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I appreciate you so much for helping me find my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.21,0:24:36.28,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并不容易  但没关系
Dialogue: 1,0:24:34.21,0:24:36.28,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I mean, it wasn't easy, but it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.50,0:24:39.38,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-我想给你个东西  -不不不
Dialogue: 1,0:24:37.50,0:24:39.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Let me give you something... - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.38,0:24:41.32,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你当我是什么慈善对象吗
Dialogue: 1,0:24:39.38,0:24:41.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You think I'm some fucking charity case?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.30,0:24:43.70,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不  吉赛尔
Dialogue: 1,0:24:42.30,0:24:43.70,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, Gizelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.76,0:24:45.66,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-我没有  -我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 1,0:24:43.76,0:24:45.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- I didn't... - I was kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.80,0:24:47.91,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:24:46.80,0:24:47.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.93,0:24:49.60,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我有那么一秒真差点信了
Dialogue: 1,0:24:47.93,0:24:49.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I actually believed you there for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.60,0:24:52.21,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道我绝不会那样伤害你的感情
Dialogue: 1,0:24:49.60,0:24:52.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You know I would never hurt your feelings like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.42,0:24:54.46,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们就去见你老爸吧
Dialogue: 1,0:24:53.42,0:24:54.46,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We'll go see your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.69,0:24:56.67,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.69,0:24:56.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.30,0:25:04.05,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来
Dialogue: 1,0:25:03.30,0:25:04.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.37,0:25:08.10,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来
Dialogue: 1,0:25:07.37,0:25:08.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.06,0:25:38.21,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到了  172号
Dialogue: 1,0:25:36.06,0:25:38.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Here it is, 172.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.48,0:25:43.09,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去找你老爸吧  妹子
Dialogue: 1,0:25:41.48,0:25:43.09,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Go on. Get your daddy, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.00,0:25:55.65,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}2号公寓  找到了
Dialogue: 1,0:25:54.00,0:25:55.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Apartment number two. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.15,0:26:25.93,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 1,0:26:25.15,0:26:25.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hola.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.14,0:26:55.71,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没想到你会来
Dialogue: 1,0:26:54.14,0:26:55.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I did not expect this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.73,0:26:58.21,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}实在是太久了
Dialogue: 1,0:26:56.73,0:26:58.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's been a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.27,0:27:00.13,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:26:59.27,0:27:00.13,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.77,0:27:04.17,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你现在都是个大姑娘了  加布里埃尔
Dialogue: 1,0:27:01.77,0:27:04.17,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You're all grown up now, Gabriela.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.28,0:27:07.43,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你怎么找到我的
Dialogue: 1,0:27:06.28,0:27:07.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.07,0:27:10.26,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不容易
Dialogue: 1,0:27:09.07,0:27:10.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It wasn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.53,0:27:14.35,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你一直很聪明
Dialogue: 1,0:27:11.53,0:27:14.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You always had a good head on your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.74,0:27:17.73,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}哪怕是小时候  你也总是学校里最优秀的
Dialogue: 1,0:27:14.74,0:27:17.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Even as a little girl, you always did good in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.50,0:27:22.15,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我得跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 1,0:27:20.50,0:27:22.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.80,0:27:27.57,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你现在看起来跟你妈妈一模一样
Dialogue: 1,0:27:24.80,0:27:27.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Just now you looked just like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.97,0:27:29.74,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 1,0:27:28.97,0:27:29.74,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.80,0:27:31.41,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的  非常像
Dialogue: 1,0:27:29.80,0:27:31.41,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yes, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.18,0:27:33.91,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你都能当她的双胞胎了
Dialogue: 1,0:27:32.18,0:27:33.91,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You could almost be her twin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.68,0:27:38.12,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢  我...我得问你一个问题
Dialogue: 1,0:27:34.68,0:27:38.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Thank you. Um, I need to... I need to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.02,0:27:40.00,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当然可以
Dialogue: 1,0:27:39.02,0:27:40.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.62,0:27:43.20,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你当初为什么离开我们
Dialogue: 1,0:27:41.62,0:27:43.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why did you leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.25,0:27:52.38,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只是想理解你为什么就那么走了
Dialogue: 1,0:27:48.25,0:27:52.38,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm just trying to understand why you would just go like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.42,0:27:55.26,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:27:54.42,0:27:55.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.68,0:28:03.39,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为有一天  我看着你和你妈妈
Dialogue: 1,0:27:59.68,0:28:03.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Because one day, I looked at your mother and you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.77,0:28:08.10,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我意识到你俩对我而言都没有任何意义了
Dialogue: 1,0:28:03.77,0:28:08.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}and realized you both didn't mean anything to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.69,0:28:11.98,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道这很难理解
Dialogue: 1,0:28:09.69,0:28:11.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I know it's hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.19,0:28:14.90,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为我浪费了太多时间
Dialogue: 1,0:28:12.19,0:28:14.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But I wasted time
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.95,0:28:18.07,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跟你在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:28:15.95,0:28:18.07,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}being with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.07,0:28:20.20,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有她
Dialogue: 1,0:28:19.07,0:28:20.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}and her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.74,0:28:25.12,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后她死了  留下我跟你一起
Dialogue: 1,0:28:21.74,0:28:25.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And she fucking dies and leaves me with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.46,0:28:29.00,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我从来就没想要你
Dialogue: 1,0:28:26.46,0:28:29.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}who I never wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.96,0:28:35.34,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有问题吗
Dialogue: 1,0:28:33.96,0:28:35.34,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Any more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.05,0:28:39.80,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你不用再回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:28:38.05,0:28:39.80,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You don't need to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.19,0:28:52.15,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么了  妹子  发生了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:28:50.19,0:28:52.15,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hey, what happened? Girl, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.15,0:28:54.78,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我应该听他的  他一直都是对的
Dialogue: 1,0:28:52.15,0:28:54.78,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I should've listened to him. He was right the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.78,0:28:56.11,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-我今晚得回家  -谁
Dialogue: 1,0:28:54.78,0:28:56.11,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- I got to get back home tonight. - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.11,0:28:57.65,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去他的  你不能开车回家
Dialogue: 1,0:28:56.11,0:28:57.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Fuck that! You're not gonna drive home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.65,0:28:59.86,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太晚了  你情绪又这么不好
Dialogue: 1,0:28:57.65,0:28:59.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's too late and you're too upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.20,0:29:03.12,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我来帮你  但你得冷静下来
Dialogue: 1,0:29:00.20,0:29:03.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yo, let me help you. You got to calm down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.79,0:29:05.95,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们得做点什么让你忘掉这些
Dialogue: 1,0:29:03.79,0:29:05.95,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We'll do something to get this out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.08,0:29:09.00,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我来开车
Dialogue: 1,0:29:08.08,0:29:09.00,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.99,0:29:43.16,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:29:41.99,0:29:43.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hi. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.44,0:32:21.23,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约翰  约翰
Dialogue: 1,0:32:19.44,0:32:21.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}John! John!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.23,0:32:24.02,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-怎么了  -她根本没去安东尼娅家
Dialogue: 1,0:32:21.23,0:32:24.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- What's the matter? - She never went to Antonia's.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.02,0:32:26.73,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-她去了墨西哥  -什么
Dialogue: 1,0:32:24.02,0:32:26.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- She went to Mexico. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.82,0:32:28.57,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吉赛尔打电话来了  加布里埃尔
Dialogue: 1,0:32:26.82,0:32:28.57,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gizelle called. Gabriela went to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.57,0:32:31.16,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去见了她爸  一直没回来
Dialogue: 1,0:32:28.57,0:32:31.16,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}see her father and never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.12,0:32:33.37,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你有地址吗
Dialogue: 1,0:32:32.12,0:32:33.37,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Did you get an address?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.74,0:32:36.08,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}还有她爸的地址
Dialogue: 1,0:32:34.74,0:32:36.08,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And her father's too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.87,0:32:39.29,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是怎么回事  约翰
Dialogue: 1,0:32:37.87,0:32:39.29,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What happened, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.83,0:32:45.71,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-我要报警吗  -警察不能越境
Dialogue: 1,0:32:42.83,0:32:45.71,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Should I call the police? - Cops can't cross the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.00,0:32:47.84,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们在那边什么也做不了
Dialogue: 1,0:32:46.00,0:32:47.84,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Down there, they don't do shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.63,0:32:49.30,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜托了  约翰
Dialogue: 1,0:32:48.63,0:32:49.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Please, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.76,0:32:51.84,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会找到她的
Dialogue: 1,0:32:50.76,0:32:51.84,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.80,0:33:28.67,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我控制不了外面的世界
Dialogue: 1,0:33:26.80,0:33:28.67,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I can't control what's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.71,0:33:31.76,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你不可能永远保护我
Dialogue: 1,0:33:29.71,0:33:31.76,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You can't just protect me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.76,0:35:22.47,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我找加布里埃尔
Dialogue: 1,0:35:20.76,0:35:22.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm looking for Gabrielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.72,0:35:24.10,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她不在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:35:22.72,0:35:24.10,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.23,0:35:30.35,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那她在哪
Dialogue: 1,0:35:29.23,0:35:30.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.52,0:35:33.44,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我什么也不知道
Dialogue: 1,0:35:31.52,0:35:33.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.48,0:35:38.65,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些破事都是因为你
Dialogue: 1,0:35:34.48,0:35:38.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}All this shit is because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.74,0:35:45.66,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我十年前就该拧断你的脖子
Dialogue: 1,0:35:41.74,0:35:45.66,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I should've broke your fucking neck ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.69,0:36:16.65,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}吉赛尔
Dialogue: 1,0:36:15.69,0:36:16.65,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gizelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.69,0:36:21.90,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我叫约翰  我们之前见过几次
Dialogue: 1,0:36:19.69,0:36:21.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}My name is John. We've met a few times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.90,0:36:24.49,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-我找加布里埃尔  -她不在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:36:21.90,0:36:24.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- I'm looking for Gabrielle. - She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.49,0:36:25.78,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道她可能在哪吗
Dialogue: 1,0:36:24.49,0:36:25.78,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do you know where she could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.24,0:36:28.62,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不知道  她找我帮忙找她父亲
Dialogue: 1,0:36:26.24,0:36:28.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't know. She wanted help finding her old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.91,0:36:29.49,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我只知道这个
Dialogue: 1,0:36:28.91,0:36:29.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}That's all I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.50,0:36:32.50,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我能问几个问题吗  关于发生的事
Dialogue: 1,0:36:29.50,0:36:32.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You mind if I ask you a few questions about what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.96,0:36:34.54,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可以  但我知道的并不多
Dialogue: 1,0:36:32.96,0:36:34.54,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay, but I don't know much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.58,0:36:36.25,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}进去说吧  如果你不介意的话
Dialogue: 1,0:36:34.58,0:36:36.25,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Inside, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.42,0:36:38.13,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:36:37.42,0:36:38.13,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.17,0:36:43.55,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她非常伤心
Dialogue: 1,0:36:42.17,0:36:43.55,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}She was so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.84,0:36:47.51,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他相当于让她滚蛋了  我只是想帮忙
Dialogue: 1,0:36:43.84,0:36:47.51,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}He basically told her to fuck off, and I just wanted to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.93,0:36:48.89,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后发生了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:36:47.93,0:36:48.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.68,0:36:50.72,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}发生了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:36:49.68,0:36:50.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.89,0:36:53.27,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她大哭了一场  让我感觉很难过
