Dialogue: 1,1:02:43.58,1:02:45.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.81,1:02:48.33,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你还有漫长的人生
Dialogue: 1,1:02:45.81,1:02:48.33,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You got so much life left.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.33,1:02:51.69,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你还有许多要做的事
Dialogue: 1,1:02:48.33,1:02:51.69,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You got so many things you got to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.41,1:02:54.01,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}许多事
Dialogue: 1,1:02:52.41,1:02:54.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}So many things.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.01,1:03:00.21,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很久之前我回家时  你那么小
Dialogue: 1,1:02:56.01,1:03:00.21,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}When I came home a long time ago, you were so young.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.21,1:03:02.12,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}加布里埃尔  你那么小
Dialogue: 1,1:03:00.21,1:03:02.12,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gabrielle, you were so young.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.56,1:03:06.84,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我很迷茫  我迷失了自我
Dialogue: 1,1:03:03.56,1:03:06.84,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I was lost. I was a lost man.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.51,1:03:10.26,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后我见到了你
Dialogue: 1,1:03:07.51,1:03:10.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And then I met you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.42,1:03:15.82,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我看到了我以为再也看不到的东西
Dialogue: 1,1:03:11.42,1:03:15.82,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And I saw something that I didn't think I'd ever see anymore:
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.41,1:03:21.32,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这世上的美好  纯真
Dialogue: 1,1:03:17.41,1:03:21.32,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Good in this world. Some innocence.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.32,1:03:25.62,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我有了一个从不敢奢望的家
Dialogue: 1,1:03:21.32,1:03:25.62,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And I had a family that I never thought I'd ever have.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.77,1:03:30.07,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抚养你长大  是我这辈子最好的事
Dialogue: 1,1:03:25.77,1:03:30.07,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And raising you, it was the best thing that ever happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.07,1:03:33.49,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为此我谢谢你  谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,1:03:30.07,1:03:33.49,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And I thank you for that. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.49,1:03:34.50,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你就像...
Dialogue: 1,1:03:33.49,1:03:34.50,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You're like the...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.16,1:03:38.90,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}加布里埃尔  加布里埃尔
Dialogue: 1,1:03:36.16,1:03:38.90,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gabrielle? Gabrielle.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.57,1:03:47.68,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}加布里埃尔  不  不
Dialogue: 1,1:03:45.57,1:03:47.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gabrielle. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.82,1:03:49.07,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别这样
Dialogue: 1,1:03:47.82,1:03:49.07,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.15,1:03:52.24,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}加布里埃尔
Dialogue: 1,1:03:51.15,1:03:52.24,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Gabrielle?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.05,1:03:56.60,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天啊
Dialogue: 1,1:03:55.05,1:03:56.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.86,1:04:16.30,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 1,1:04:14.86,1:04:16.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.71,1:04:31.43,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么不是我
Dialogue: 1,1:04:29.71,1:04:31.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why not me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.95,1:05:24.86,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 1,1:05:23.95,1:05:24.86,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.12,1:07:03.20,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我希望你住在你妹妹家
Dialogue: 1,1:07:01.12,1:07:03.20,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want you to stay at your sister's.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.69,1:07:07.76,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这里没什么让你留恋的了  我也没有
Dialogue: 1,1:07:04.69,1:07:07.76,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}There's nothing for you here, nothing for me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.22,1:07:10.61,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你要去哪
Dialogue: 1,1:07:09.22,1:07:10.61,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Where will you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.96,1:07:13.80,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我四处漂泊
Dialogue: 1,1:07:11.96,1:07:13.80,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm just gonna move around.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.37,1:07:16.84,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一如往常
Dialogue: 1,1:07:15.37,1:07:16.84,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Like always.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.38,1:07:19.85,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我还会再见到你吗
Dialogue: 1,1:07:18.38,1:07:19.85,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Will I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.63,1:07:23.59,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会的
Dialogue: 1,1:07:22.63,1:07:23.59,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.99,1:07:30.47,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会想念这里
Dialogue: 1,1:07:28.99,1:07:30.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I will miss this.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.16,1:08:01.07,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 1,1:08:00.16,1:08:01.07,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.66,1:08:07.18,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一路顺风
Dialogue: 1,1:08:05.66,1:08:07.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Travel safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.72,1:11:33.81,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想要什么
Dialogue: 1,1:11:32.72,1:11:33.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.85,1:11:35.93,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 1,1:11:34.85,1:11:35.93,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.81,1:11:37.73,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}进来
Dialogue: 1,1:11:36.81,1:11:37.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.85,1:11:43.47,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果有人看到你  我们两个都会死
Dialogue: 1,1:11:40.85,1:11:43.47,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If someone sees you, we both will die.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.02,1:11:46.06,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}回来这里太危险了
Dialogue: 1,1:11:44.02,1:11:46.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Coming back here is so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.68,1:11:47.77,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你找到她了吗
Dialogue: 1,1:11:46.68,1:11:47.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.02,1:11:49.36,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她死了
Dialogue: 1,1:11:48.02,1:11:49.36,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.56,1:11:54.43,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我...
Dialogue: 1,1:11:53.56,1:11:54.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.31,1:11:56.19,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我很遗憾
Dialogue: 1,1:11:55.31,1:11:56.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.64,1:12:00.14,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真的  我明白你的感觉
Dialogue: 1,1:11:57.64,1:12:00.14,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I really am. I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.22,1:12:04.35,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但回来真的很危险
Dialogue: 1,1:12:01.22,1:12:04.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But coming back was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.31,1:12:06.64,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你为什么来
Dialogue: 1,1:12:05.31,1:12:06.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.52,1:12:09.64,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想找到那个瘦子
Dialogue: 1,1:12:07.52,1:12:09.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I wanna find the thin one.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.01,1:12:12.01,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-不  -伤她那个人
Dialogue: 1,1:12:10.01,1:12:12.01,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- No. - The one that cut her.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.01,1:12:13.85,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-不  -伤我那个人
Dialogue: 1,1:12:12.01,1:12:13.85,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- No. - The one that cut me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.14,1:12:16.64,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不会再帮你
Dialogue: 1,1:12:14.14,1:12:16.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I will not help you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.64,1:12:17.69,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你必须帮我
Dialogue: 1,1:12:16.64,1:12:17.69,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.85,1:12:19.19,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 1,1:12:17.85,1:12:19.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why do I have to?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.84,1:12:23.02,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这能改变什么  什么也改变不了
Dialogue: 1,1:12:19.84,1:12:23.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What will it change? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.89,1:12:26.81,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们悲痛然后继续生活
Dialogue: 1,1:12:23.89,1:12:26.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We grieve and move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.94,1:12:29.19,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你做到了吗
Dialogue: 1,1:12:27.94,1:12:29.19,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And you've done that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.01,1:12:35.81,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我每天都会想她
Dialogue: 1,1:12:32.01,1:12:35.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I mean, I think of her every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.10,1:12:37.98,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}该死的每一天
Dialogue: 1,1:12:36.10,1:12:37.98,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Every fucking day.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.76,1:12:42.60,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我们必须向前看
Dialogue: 1,1:12:40.76,1:12:42.60,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But we have to move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.97,1:12:44.81,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果不能呢
Dialogue: 1,1:12:42.97,1:12:44.81,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What if you can't move on?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.27,1:12:47.68,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}-如果完全不能呢  -可你必须那么做
Dialogue: 1,1:12:45.27,1:12:47.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- What if you can't move on at all? - But you have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.69,1:12:50.05,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们别无选择  过去的已经过去了
Dialogue: 1,1:12:47.69,1:12:50.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We have no choice. What's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.05,1:12:51.26,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为什么过去了
Dialogue: 1,1:12:50.05,1:12:51.26,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why is it done?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.56,1:12:55.06,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么可能过去
Dialogue: 1,1:12:52.56,1:12:55.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}How is it ever done?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.73,1:13:00.30,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我看到她那张纯真的脸
Dialogue: 1,1:12:56.73,1:13:00.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}When I look at something so innocent...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.39,1:13:04.89,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}永远地失去了生命
Dialogue: 1,1:13:01.39,1:13:04.89,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}and I see that face never have life in it again,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.93,1:13:09.72,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么可能过去
Dialogue: 1,1:13:04.93,1:13:09.72,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}how is it ever done?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.01,1:13:13.77,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要复仇
Dialogue: 1,1:13:12.01,1:13:13.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want revenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.06,1:13:19.02,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要让他们知道死期到了
Dialogue: 1,1:13:15.06,1:13:19.02,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want them to know that death is coming...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.97,1:13:24.27,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们做什么都无济于事
Dialogue: 1,1:13:19.97,1:13:24.27,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}and there's nothing they can do to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.35,1:13:28.44,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要让他们感受到我们的悲痛
Dialogue: 1,1:13:25.35,1:13:28.44,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want them to feel our grief...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.30,1:13:34.23,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并且知道那是他们人生最后的感觉
Dialogue: 1,1:13:29.30,1:13:34.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}and know that's the last thing they will ever feel.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.23,1:13:38.35,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道你也想这样
Dialogue: 1,1:13:36.23,1:13:38.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And I know you want it too.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.01,1:15:50.85,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去吧
Dialogue: 1,1:15:50.01,1:15:50.85,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.19,1:18:11.06,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抓住他  这个外国佬不算什么
Dialogue: 1,1:18:08.19,1:18:11.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Get him! This old gringo is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.56,1:24:16.56,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这边
Dialogue: 1,1:24:15.56,1:24:16.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Here!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.14,1:25:00.30,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们都死了
Dialogue: 1,1:24:59.14,1:25:00.30,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.35,1:25:02.35,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所有人
Dialogue: 1,1:25:01.35,1:25:02.35,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.47,1:25:05.56,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我本可以杀你十次
Dialogue: 1,1:25:03.47,1:25:05.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I could've killed you ten times.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.89,1:25:08.40,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我想把你留到最后
Dialogue: 1,1:25:06.89,1:25:08.40,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But I wanted you last.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.55,1:25:10.97,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你去死
Dialogue: 1,1:25:09.55,1:25:10.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.14,1:25:13.39,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不  你去死  你死定了
Dialogue: 1,1:25:11.14,1:25:13.39,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, fuck you, dead man.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.77,1:25:18.97,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想要你在被我剖胸挖心时
Dialogue: 1,1:25:14.77,1:25:18.97,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want you to feel my rage, my hate,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.01,1:25:24.77,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}感受我的愤怒  我的仇恨
Dialogue: 1,1:25:20.01,1:25:24.77,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}when I reach into your chest and rip out your heart!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.14,1:25:27.56,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就像你对我做的那样
Dialogue: 1,1:25:26.14,1:25:27.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Like you did mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.43,1:25:33.68,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想活吗
Dialogue: 1,1:25:32.43,1:25:33.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You want to live?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.39,1:25:35.73,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}跟着灯光
Dialogue: 1,1:25:34.39,1:25:35.73,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Follow the lights.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.64,1:28:04.68,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 1,1:28:02.64,1:28:04.68,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This is what it feels like.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.85,1:29:03.64,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我一直活在死亡的世界
Dialogue: 1,1:29:00.85,1:29:03.64,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I've lived in a world of death.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.97,1:29:07.06,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我曾尝试回家
Dialogue: 1,1:29:04.97,1:29:07.06,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I tried to come home,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.48,1:29:10.05,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但从未真正回到家
Dialogue: 1,1:29:07.48,1:29:10.05,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}but I never really arrived.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.97,1:29:14.56,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的一部分精神和灵魂
Dialogue: 1,1:29:10.97,1:29:14.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}A part of my mind and soul...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.27,1:29:17.56,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在途中迷失了
Dialogue: 1,1:29:15.27,1:29:17.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}got lost along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.80,1:29:23.22,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我的心仍在这里
Dialogue: 1,1:29:19.80,1:29:23.22,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But my heart was still here,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.56,1:29:25.56,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我出生的地方
Dialogue: 1,1:29:23.56,1:29:25.56,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}where I was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.60,1:29:29.43,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会一直守护到死的地方
Dialogue: 1,1:29:26.60,1:29:29.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Where I would defend to the end...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.39,1:29:33.18,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我仅有的家人
Dialogue: 1,1:29:30.39,1:29:33.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}the only family I've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.10,1:29:37.94,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我仅有的家
Dialogue: 1,1:29:35.10,1:29:37.94,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The only home I've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.43,1:29:44.18,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我爱的人现在都已逝去
Dialogue: 1,1:29:40.43,1:29:44.18,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}All the ones I've loved are now ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.43,1:29:48.23,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但我会拼命
Dialogue: 1,1:29:46.43,1:29:48.23,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But I will fight...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.09,1:29:52.43,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让他们的记忆长存
Dialogue: 1,1:29:50.09,1:29:52.43,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}to keep their memories alive...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.18,1:29:55.31,中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}直到永远
Dialogue: 1,1:29:54.18,1:29:55.31,英文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}forever.








Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:44.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}天文台已将“天马”上升为2级风暴
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.28,0:00:44.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}NWS has upgraded the storm Telmar to a category 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:48.03,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}预计有大雨及风速会达到每小时85公里
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.02,0:00:48.03,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Heavy rain and wind speed up to 85 mph are to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.38,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我是沙漠之鹰 仍然没有看见三名失踪的登山者
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.38,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This is Desert Eagle. Still no visual on the 3 missing hikers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:55.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}B对 C队 请与国民警卫队确认是否继续救援行动
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.60,0:00:55.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Bravo, Charlie, please confirm CIS with rescue ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}快点
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.93,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}LC队 我是救援一队
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.93,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This is Rescue Team One, Lima Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们的警犬不擅长搜索登山者 同时这里变得越来越糟
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Our dogs are negative on the hikers, but it's getting worse down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:05.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 风暴正在加速 - 沙漠之鹰 现时状况如何?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.87,0:01:05.92,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Storm is speeding up. - Desert Eagle, what's the status up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:09.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}洪水贯穿大楼 叫你的兄弟们离开这座山 完毕
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.22,0:01:09.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}There is a flood throughout building. Gonna get your guys off the mountain. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:14.49,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所有队伍都移往高地 山洪来了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.76,0:01:14.49,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}All teams to higher ground. Big fall of water coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:17.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}营救行动撤消 尽快寻求栖身地
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.64,0:01:17.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Rescue ops - retreat or seek shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:20.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那名骑马的志愿者在哪里?无线电联系不上他
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.56,0:01:20.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Where's that volunteer on horse back? He's not on radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:24.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他应该在返回途中 疯了才会下山去
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.66,0:01:24.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}He's gotta be on his way back. He'd be crazy to downhill this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:32.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}洪水流窜不定 我们回来前把他叫回
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.53,0:01:32.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Too much turbulence. We bring it in before we're back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:17.53,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嘿 嘿 - 嘿 这里
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.32,0:02:17.53,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Hey! Hey! - Hey. Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 救救我们 - 嘿
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Help us! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}水流乱窜 洪水快来了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}The water is going. There is a lot of water coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.65,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}上来
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.31,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我和妻子一起来的 见过我妻子吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.08,0:02:26.31,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm here with my wife. Have you seen my wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:29.30,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 快上来 - 你要我们走 她可能就在山下
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.31,0:02:29.30,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Come on. Get on. - You got us go and she could be right down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:32.90,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没在那里 我在河下游找到了她 她已死了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.45,0:02:32.90,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}She's not. I found her down the river. She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 杰米 走吧 - 我要去找她
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.90,0:02:36.15,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Please, Jaime, let's go! - I'm gonna go find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}杰米
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Jaime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:49.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}下来吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.19,0:02:49.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Come on down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:52.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去那块大石那边
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.39,0:02:52.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Get over that round rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.87,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}快点 小伙子
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.87,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Come on, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}靠近点儿 尽量握紧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Get in close. Hold as tight as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.14,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们会死吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.14,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Are we gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.91,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你从哪儿找到他们的呢? - 峡谷两英哩下游处
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.91,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- So where did you find them? - 2 miles down stream at Base Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.92,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 确认身份了吗? - 还没 有点难度
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.92,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Did you get a positive ID? - Not yet, it's pretty torn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嘿 他是谁?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hey, who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:15.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}长期志愿服务者 上尉
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.80,0:04:15.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Volunteers from time to time, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.94,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们人手不足 他可是名追踪高手
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.94,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nam burning op, but he's a hell of a tracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:20.04,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你还好吗 约翰?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.97,0:04:20.04,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You alright, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}妻子在第一波洪水中就死了 丈夫跑去找她了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Wife got killed in the first wave, husband ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的 我们在下游约一英哩处发现了他们
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yeah, we found them about a mile down the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.98,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你已经尽你所能了 约翰
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.98,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You did what you could, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.37,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们再次感谢您的帮助
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.37,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And we appreciate your help, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.60,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嘿 先生
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.60,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hey, Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.64,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.64,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.22,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不客气
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.22,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好小子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.77,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你累了吗? - 是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.77,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Are you tired? - I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你一定冻坏了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You must be freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}热咖啡可以帮你暖暖身子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hot coffee will help you warm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.65,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我听了新闻报导
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I heard the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.46,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}两人死亡
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.46,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Two people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:09.28,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}无法救他们
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.81,0:06:09.28,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Couldn't save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.70,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}也救不了在战争中的兄弟们
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.44,0:06:12.70,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Couldn't save my brothers in the war either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不要责怪你自己 因为当时你要救另一些人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You cannot blame yourself because you gonna save some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你已不在战争中了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You are not in the war anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.62,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}战争只存在你的脑海里
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.62,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Only in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.25,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是很难忘掉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.25,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's hard to turn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.65,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}坐在那里 你让我想起了你的父亲
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sitting there, you remind me of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.85,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他会坐在外面的摇椅上
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.85,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}He would sit outside, in his rocking chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:43.44,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一直冥想 从不说话
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.43,0:06:43.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Always thinking, never talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但你在这有一份不错的工作
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}But you have done a wonderful job here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.09,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}打理这个地方
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.09,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Running this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我很感激你让我留下来
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I can't thank you enough for letting me stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.41,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并帮助加布里艾拉成长
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.41,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And helping raise Gabriella.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.02,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.02,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}晚安 玛丽亚
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Good night, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 推 - 好的 天啦
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.13,0:11:52.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Push - Okay, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.13,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 铰链要加润滑油 - 我可以帮把手
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.13,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Have to grease theses hinges. - I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 昨晚怎么样?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Okay. How did it go last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.11,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}参加派对的人并不多
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.11,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Well, not that many poople showed up to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 为什么? - 因为下雨
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Why not? - Because of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}祖母已告诉我 昨晚所发生的事
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Grandma told me what happened last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}关于死去的人
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}About the people who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:14.57,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你还好吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.94,0:12:14.57,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.29,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道这不是你的错 对吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.27,0:12:18.29,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You know it's not your fault, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.23,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你尽力了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.23,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.15,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我确实尽力了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.01,0:12:23.15,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I did try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.10,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想去骑马吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.10,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do you want to go to ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.88,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 去穿上你的靴子 - 好
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.88,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Yeah, go puts your boots on. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.71,0:29:54.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嗨 - 嗨
Dialogue: 1,0:29:50.71,0:29:54.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.36,0:30:30.35,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}唐 米高
Dialogue: 1,0:30:29.36,0:30:30.35,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Don Miguel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.78,0:30:33.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谢谢你的到来
Dialogue: 1,0:30:31.78,0:30:33.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.30,0:30:35.86,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想喝点什么吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:30:34.30,0:30:35.86,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do you want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.08,0:30:38.68,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我时间不多 - 那就直接谈生意吧
Dialogue: 1,0:30:36.08,0:30:38.68,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- I don't have much time. - Let's go straight to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.89,0:30:43.89,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我听说你想拓展业务
Dialogue: 1,0:30:41.89,0:30:43.89,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I heard you want to expand your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.01,0:30:47.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的 公司需要成长
Dialogue: 1,0:30:45.01,0:30:47.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I want to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.22,0:30:51.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}与你合作 我就能成功 我们会是最佳拍档
Dialogue: 1,0:30:47.22,0:30:51.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}With your help I can achieve that. We'd be partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.17,0:30:52.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我一直在寻找新的少女
Dialogue: 1,0:30:51.17,0:30:52.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I always look for new whores.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.60,0:30:57.65,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去年我已经输出了超过一万七千名女孩
Dialogue: 1,0:30:53.60,0:30:57.65,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I've exported more than 17 000 girls last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.65,0:31:01.47,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即使是丑的 也可以让我们盈利超过三十万
Dialogue: 1,0:30:57.65,0:31:01.47,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Even the ugliest ones, can make us more than 300 000.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.62,0:31:09.33,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}唐 米高 你看起来很不错啊
Dialogue: 1,0:31:06.62,0:31:09.33,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Don Miguel, you look perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.19,0:31:11.32,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}走远点
Dialogue: 1,0:31:10.19,0:31:11.32,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.56,0:31:15.78,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道你喜欢我们的女孩 他们质量是最好的
Dialogue: 1,0:31:11.56,0:31:15.78,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I knew you would like our girls. They are of the best quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.84,0:31:18.84,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我听说你发了一批货往纽约
Dialogue: 1,0:31:16.84,0:31:18.84,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I heard you sent a shipment to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.60,0:31:21.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}走开 维达
Dialogue: 1,0:31:19.60,0:31:21.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Leave us, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.19,0:31:23.00,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我需要跟米高谈谈
Dialogue: 1,0:31:21.19,0:31:23.00,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I need to speak to Miguel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.62,0:31:26.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就在这里说啊 有什么问题吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:23.62,0:31:26.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}So speak here. What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.18,0:31:31.01,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雨果 谁管理那地方 你俩商量好以后 请通知我
Dialogue: 1,0:31:27.18,0:31:31.01,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Hugo, after you guys decide who runs the place, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.21,0:31:33.42,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}请给我一分钟 唐 米高
Dialogue: 1,0:31:31.21,0:31:33.42,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Please give me a minute, Don Miguel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.92,0:31:35.80,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}维达
Dialogue: 1,0:31:34.92,0:31:35.80,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.34,0:31:39.82,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你怎么回事?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:37.34,0:31:39.82,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.94,0:31:42.27,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道什么是业务吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:39.94,0:31:42.27,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do you know what's on the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.70,0:31:45.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在说什么?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:43.70,0:31:45.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.93,0:31:48.66,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的工作就是 找到最好的妓女
Dialogue: 1,0:31:45.93,0:31:48.66,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I work my ass off, getting the best whores.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.66,0:31:50.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而谈生意时 我居然不能在场?
Dialogue: 1,0:31:48.66,0:31:50.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And I cannot be present when business is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.44,0:31:53.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你这样让我很没面子
Dialogue: 1,0:31:50.44,0:31:53.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.85,0:31:56.63,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 放松点 - 闭上你的嘴 蠢驴
Dialogue: 1,0:31:53.85,0:31:56.63,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- Go easy. - Shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.73,0:32:00.05,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这不是玩的时候 也不是玩的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:31:57.73,0:32:00.05,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}This is not the time, nor place to play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.08,0:32:02.56,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}业务上有很多钱要赚
Dialogue: 1,0:32:00.08,0:32:02.56,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}There is a lot of money on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.76,0:32:05.44,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你谈你的业务
Dialogue: 1,0:32:03.76,0:32:05.44,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You do your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.44,0:32:07.17,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会尽我所能
Dialogue: 1,0:32:05.44,0:32:07.17,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}and I'll do mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.66,0:32:10.18,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不好意思 失陪
Dialogue: 1,0:32:08.66,0:32:10.18,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.93,0:45:09.39,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开始吧 他们都是你们的了 玩得开心点
Dialogue: 1,0:45:06.93,0:45:09.39,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Let's go! They are all yours! Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.21,0:51:19.50,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在开玩笑吗?
Dialogue: 1,0:51:18.21,0:51:19.50,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You think I'm stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.55,0:51:22.26,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没人跟你开玩笑
Dialogue: 1,0:51:20.55,0:51:22.26,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}No, I don't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.41,0:51:26.81,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你当然有 我想马上杀了他 但你却跟他玩
Dialogue: 1,0:51:22.41,0:51:26.81,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I wanted to kill him straight away and you didn't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.89,0:51:28.08,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你简直都快成了爱玩的大男孩
Dialogue: 1,0:51:26.89,0:51:28.08,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You embarassed me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.22,0:51:29.19,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你想要什么?
Dialogue: 1,0:51:28.22,0:51:29.19,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.06,0:51:32.96,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想他死
Dialogue: 1,0:51:32.06,0:51:32.96,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Give me his girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.04,0:51:39.06,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 这是门生意 - 我知道 但我还是想杀了他
Dialogue: 1,0:51:35.04,0:51:39.06,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- This is business. - I know, but now it's personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.06,0:51:46.16,中文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:51:45.06,0:51:46.16,英文,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Alright.
